<div id="pf41b9" class="pf w51 h2f0" data-page-no="41b9"><div class="pc pc41b9 w51 h2f0"><div class="t m755 x0 h5 y2974 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 9 February 26 to March 4 </div><div class="t m77b xb7 h21c y28c2 ff3 fs41 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Ciedort </div><div class="t m1bd3 xc4 h21c y1f65 ff3 fs41 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lad Cali </div><div class="t m271 x15 h5 y191e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Saying with a loud voice, Fear God, </div><div class="t m3e1 xb7 h5 y1ff4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t me75 x26 h35 y1ff4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">give glory to </div><div class="t m9c3 x10 h5 y1e81 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him; for the hour of </div><div class="t m837 xb7 h5 y20dc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hisjudgment is come: and worship </div><div class="t m304 xb7 h5 y1fc3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him that made heaven, and earth, and </div><div class="t m179 xb7 h5 y680 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sea, and the fountains of waters&quot; </div><div class="t m2b0 xb7 h5 y1ef0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 14:7). </div><div class="t m433 x15 h35 y1aed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The developing interest in the topic </div><div class="t m821 xb7 h35 y1f9e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Creation, seen in the controversies </div><div class="t m144 xb7 h35 y1ad1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">over the teaching of Creation in public </div><div class="t m15a3 xb7 h35 y173a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">schools and in the proliferation of </div><div class="t maa4 xb7 h35 y208a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">journals and societies devoted to the </div><div class="t ma50 xb7 h35 y11a4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study and promotion of Creation, </div><div class="t m81f xb7 h35 y1d14 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should be of great interest to </div><div class="t m59a xb7 h35 y202e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Seventh-day Adventists. </div><div class="t m141 x15 h35 y1e52 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Two of the three messages </div><div class="t m2e6 xb7 h35 y1da5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">proclaimed by the angels in Revelation </div><div class="t m222 x0 h35 y184e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14 have a very direct bearing upon the </div><div class="t m9e2 xb7 h35 y1a4a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">topic of Creation and God as Creator. </div><div class="t ma78 xb7 h35 y16b5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Since it is our belief that the messages </div><div class="t m10a xb7 h35 y1b9b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of these three angels will constitute in </div><div class="t m589 x0 h35 y214c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the time of the end an important and </div><div class="t m71d xb7 h35 y1f26 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">widespread religious call to return to </div><div class="t m71e xb7 h35 y2158 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the worship of God, we watch with </div><div class="t m699 xb7 h35 y20b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">interest and satisfaction the present </div><div class="t m95 x0 h35 y19ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fulfilling of the predictions concerning </div><div class="t m297 x0 h35 y1f21 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the loud cry of these three messages. </div><div class="t m217 x15 h35 y219c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Seventh-day Adventists understand </div><div class="t m879 x0 h35 y16d4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that the Sabbath, the day that is set </div><div class="t m2b8 xb7 h35 y1e8a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">aside for the worship of God, will be </div><div class="t mf54 x0 h35 y138f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the central point of religious </div><div class="t m5ce xb7 h35 y1965 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">controversy just before the second </div><div class="t me9f xb7 h35 y1c34 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">coming of Christ. Since the Sabbath is </div><div class="t m178 xb7 h35 y1be6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">so intimately connected with the </div><div class="t m8fd x0 h35 y14f9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creation event, it is obvious that no </div><div class="t m41e xb7 h35 y1b19 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">real issue concerning Saturday and </div><div class="t m13a x0 h35 y1d66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sunday can develop or be resolved </div><div class="t m2dc xb7 h35 y1666 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">without a renewed study of the  </div><div class="t m12b x72 h35 y2135 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">creative power of God as </div><div class="t m876 x72 h35 y13d3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">demonstrated in the Creation of this </div><div class="t m89f x8f h35 y1644 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">world. </div><div class="t m9b4 x72 h5 y1ed7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x72 h5 y19af ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m5fd xbc h5 y19af ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Caller </div><div class="t m4ff xbc h5 y1b97 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 1:8, 18) </div><div class="t m558 x72 h5 y1354 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m99 x6e h5 y1b29 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lines of Communication </div><div class="t m6ab xbc h5 y2146 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 1:1) </div><div class="t mb7 x72 h5 y633 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t mda xbc h5 y1e59 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Worship of the Creator </div><div class="t m9b9 xbc h5 y2040 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 14:7) </div><div class="t m1ce x72 h5 y16cb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m34b x6e h5 y1d87 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Fall of Babylon </div><div class="t m9b9 xbc h5 y1faf ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 14:8) </div><div class="t m8a8 x72 h5 y12f6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m698 x6e h5 y1a47 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Beast, Image, and Mark </div><div class="t m82e xbc h5 y16b3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 14:9, 10) </div><div class="t m2ef x72 h5 y13f9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t maf6 xbc h5 y1b9a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Secret of Victory </div><div class="t m9f9 xbc h5 y141c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 15:2-4) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
